reviewText: Movie arrived quickly and although it's not a "best seller" , it was PERFECT gift because my husband was in it... Looked for it for years... Couldn't be more pleased
this is a good comedy movie. this is really a good movie for your collection.  I think that you should buy this.

"Rockin' Road Trip" is director William Olsen's fun-filled, fast paced romp through the South with the band "Cherry Suicide." The sound track alone makes this film worth buying! It's a cornucopia of great alternative tracks that hold up surprisingly well. This film reveals the fun and innocence of that period better than most of its 80s peers.
